# This directory holds The Lounge's runtime state when bind-mounted via
# docker-compose. Everything is local-only EXCEPT the custom theme under
# themes/hexbot/, which ships with the repo and is bind-mounted into the
# container at /var/opt/thelounge/packages/node_modules/thelounge-theme-hexbot.
*
!.gitignore
!themes/
!themes/hexbot/
!themes/hexbot/**
